                                <h3><b>Ready to Become a Campus Ambassador?</b></h3>
                                <p>Campus Ambassadors are some of the most influential people on your campus. As an Ambassador, you help us, The <b>hack.init()</b> Team, market and promote our events amongst your classmates and friends. Campus Ambassadors can play an important role in the marketing and promotion of <b>hack.init()</b>.</p>
                                <p>Being a Campus Ambassador is a fun, varied and flexible job. People who are excited about the chance to share the <b>hack.init()</b> events and to gain marketing experiences are encouraged to apply.</p>
                                <p>If you have any questions, email us at <a href="mailto:contact@hackinit.org">contact@hackinit.org</a>.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 description" if(data.lang==="zh")>
                                <h3><b>准备好成为一名校园大使了吗？</b></h3>
                                <p>作为学校里最有影响力的少数派，你将会担负起一份对我们来说万分重要的责任——帮助我们在同学和朋友中推广<b>hack.init()</b>。</p>
                                <p>当然，这是一份轻松有趣，充满弹性的工作。如果你对即将到来的挑战充满信心，或是渴望历练一下自己的市场推广技能，那么我们诚挚欢迎你的加入。</p>
                                <p>如果你有任何相关的问题，欢迎发送邮件到<a href="mailto:contact@hackinit.org">contact@hackinit.org</a>。</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 reasons" if(data.lang==="en")>
